/*.jpeg
/scratchpad/
# alphaTab's bundled soundfont + its notices are copied into public/soundfont/
# by the vite plugin on every dev/build. FluidR3Mono_GM.sf3 (the soundfont we
# actually use) is committed; these are regenerated artifacts.
apps/web/public/soundfont/sonivox.sf2
apps/web/public/soundfont/sonivox.sf3
apps/web/public/soundfont/LICENSE
apps/web/public/soundfont/README.md
